function Start(idActorKiller, idActorKilled)
	Hydra.BossEncounterManuallyComplete(idLevelArea)
	--Play Boss Victory Stinger
	Hydra.MusicOverride("DGN_Scos_MarinersRefuge", "Music_Boss_SeaHag_Victory")

	--Wait for Stinger to resolve and Reset Dungeon Music
	Hydra.Wait(10)
	Hydra.ClearMusicOverride("DGN_Scos_MarinersRefuge")
	
end

function Start(idActor, idActorDetector)
	
	--Get level area and delete trigger
	idLevelArea = Hydra.ActorGetLevelArea(idActorDetector)
	Hydra.ActorDelete(idActorDetector)
	
	--Start Boss Fight
	Hydra.BossEncounterManuallyQueueStart(idLevelArea)
	
	--Play Boss Music
	Hydra.MusicOverride("DGN_Scos_MarinersRefuge", "Music_Boss_SeaHag_Phase1")
	
end
